    "explanation": "Dutch National Flag algorithm with three pointers.",
    "answer": "def sortColors(nums):\n    l, mid, r = 0, 0, len(nums)-1\n    while mid <= r:\n        if nums[mid] == 0: nums[l], nums[mid] = nums[mid], nums[l]; l += 1; mid += 1\n        elif nums[mid] == 1: mid += 1\n        else: nums[mid], nums[r] = nums[r], nums[mid]; r -= 1",
